lead_paragraph: After three consecutive victories, Michigan State has reached a break in its schedule, and the Spartans will have five days off before facing rival Michigan next weekend.

headline.print_headline: Michigan State Makes 17 3-Pointers in 96-62 Win Over Rutgers
